Feature: Categories
    As a user of AGI
    I want to easily navigate through different categories on the website
    So that I can find relevant information about AGI's products, services, and offerings

    Background:
    Given I am on the AGI homepage


    Scenario: View information about the Institutional category
    When I click on the Institutional category in the navigation menu
    Then I should be taken to a page to check the AGis institutional background

    Scenario: View information about the Products category
    When I click on the Products category in the navigation menu
    Then I should be taken to a page where I can see the AGI's products

    Scenario: View information about the Services category
    When I click on the Services category in the navigation menu
    Then I should be taken to a page that provides info about AGI's services

    Scenario: View information about the Financial category
    When I click on the Financial category in the navigation menu
    Then I should be taken to a page to check info about finance

    Scenario: View information about the Careers category
    When I click on the Careers category in the navigation menu
    Then I should be taken to a page that talks about carrers

    Scenario: View information about the YouTube channel
    When I click on the YouTube channel category in the navigation menu
    Then I should be taken to a page to see the AGI's youtube channel

    Scenario: View information about the Investment category
    When I click on the Investment category in the navigation menu
    Then I should be taken to a page so I can see news about Investment

    Scenario: View information about the Security category
    When I click on the Security category in the navigation menu
    Then I should be taken to a page to check the news about security